OL,7,FCrafty Britons are tackling the soaring
OL,8,Fcost of living by adopting a 'Make Do
OL,9,Fand Mend' approach to their wardrobes,
OL,10,Fgiving clothing a new lease of life by
OL,11,Frepairing, altering and dyeing garments
OL,12,Fto extend their lifespan and save cash.
OL,14,FThe cost of living crisis, coupled with
OL,15,Fa growing awareness about the
OL,16,Fenvironmental damage caused by the
OL,17,Ffashion industry, has prompted
OL,18,Fresourceful Britons to pick up a needle
OL,19,Fand thread and learn skills ranging
OL,20,Ffrom darning socks to sewing entire
OL,21,Fgarments from scratch.
OL,3,CDarning socks and dyeing clothes: the
OL,4,Crise of 'make do and mend' in the cost
